com.discoverydns.dnsapiclient.command.message

Class MessageGetResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.discoverydns.dnsapiclient.command.message.MessageGetResponse
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MessageAcknowledgeResponse

    public class MessageGetResponse
extends Object
    Response object received by the DNSAPIClient from the DNSAPI server subsequently to the sending of a MessageGetCommand, describing the details of the retrieved Message. A Message is a notification from the DNSAPI server, for the targeted sponsor Account's Users, offering information about changes performed by the server on a related object in the system.
    Author:
    Chris Wright
